AN ACT making an appropriation to and authorizing the expenditure of money
by the Department of Taxation for the continued development and
implementation of the Unified Tax System; and providing other
matters properly relating thereto.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, REPRESENTED IN
SENATE AND ASSEMBLY, DO ENACT AS FOLLOWS:
1 Section 1. 1. There is hereby appropriated from the State General Fund to
2 the Department of Taxation for the continued development and implementation of
3 the Unified Tax System the following sums:
4 For the Fiscal Year 2025-2026 ........................... [$14,354,616] $12,457,960
5 For the Fiscal Year 2026-2027 ................................................... $15,281,906
6 2. Expenditure of $5,000,000 not appropriated from the State General
7 Fund or the State Highway Fund is hereby authorized during Fiscal Year
8 2025-2026 and Fiscal Year 2026-2027 by the Department of Taxation for the
9 same purpose as set forth in subsection 1.
10 3. Any balance of the sums appropriated by subsection 1 remaining at the
11 end of the respective fiscal years must not be committed for expenditure after June
12 30 of the respective fiscal years by the entity to which the appropriation is made or
13 any entity to which money from the appropriation is granted or otherwise
14 transferred in any manner, and any portion of the appropriated money remaining
15 must not be spent for any purpose after September 18, 2026, and September 17,
16 2027, respectively, by either the entity to which the money was appropriated or the
17 entity to which the money was subsequently granted or transferred, and must be

